[vc_row css=”.vc_custom_1545307641157{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}”][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=”top-to-bottom”]

ASNU takes pride in its Projetos Especiais division, offering exemplary design services that cater to the most discerning clientele.

[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” css=”.vc_custom_1550384824998{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}”][vc_column width=”1/2″ css_animation=”bottom-to-top” el_class=”image-air”][vc_single_image image=”13827″ img_size=”full” css=”.vc_custom_1738068529497{margin-left: -175px !important;}”][/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/2″ css_animation=”bottom-to-top” css=”.vc_custom_1550384738451{margin-top: -50px !important;}”][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1714055334978{padding-top: 55px !important;}”]

Our standout areas of expertise lies in fuel systems, which we have meticulously engineered and supplied to some of the world’s most exclusive supercars. The company’s cutting-edge technology and meticulous attention to detail ensure that every fuel system meets the highest standards of performance, reliability, and efficiency. By collaborating closely with prestigious automotive manufacturers and utilizing their vast experience, ASNU continues to push boundaries and set new benchmarks in the realm of automotive design.

[/vc_column_text]

  • Bespoke Motorsports Performance Diagnostics
  • Special Performance & Diagnostic Services
  • Leveraging our 30 years experience of building injector performance diagnosis
  • Research & Development Services & Expertise
[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row_content_no_spaces” full_height=”yes” columns_placement=”bottom” content_placement=”bottom” thegem_fix_full_height=”true” css=”.vc_custom_1708444811944{margin-bottom: 0px !important;background: #171b2d url(https://www.asnu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ASNU-Special-Projects.jpg?id=1261) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}” custom_css_code=”LmN1c3RvbS1kaXZpZGVyJTdCJTBBJTIwJTIwJTIwJTIwd2lkdGglM0ElMjAzOHB4JTNCJTBBJTdEJTBBJTQwbWVkaWElMjAlMjhtYXgtd2lkdGglM0ElMjAzMzBweCUyOSU3QiUwQSUyMCUyMCUyMCUyMC50aXRsZS14bGFyZ2UlMjAlN0IlMEElMjAlMjAlMjAlMjAlMjAlMjAlMjAlMjBmb250LXNpemUlM0ElMjAzNHB4JTNCJTBBJTIwJTIwJTIwJTIwJTdEJTBBJTdE”][vc_column disable_custom_paddings_mobile=”true” css=”.vc_custom_1585341316548{padding-bottom: 115px !important;padding-left: 114px !important;}”][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708444896244{margin-bottom: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}”]

ASNU Projetos Especiais division

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708444950104{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}” css_animation=”none” el_class=”t-xlarge”]

Performance

[/vc_column_text]

[vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708444927381{margin-top: 35px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}” css_animation=”none” el_class=”line-before-text”]

Acheiving Peak Performance.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” equal_height=”yes” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1589462960207{margin-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #b6c6c9 !important;}” custom_css_code=”JTQwbWVkaWElMjAlMjhtYXgtd2lkdGglM0ElMjAxMTk5cHglMjklN0IlMEEud3BiX3JvdyUzRSUyQSUyMCU3QiUwQSUyMCUyMCUyMCUyMG1hcmdpbi10b3AlM0ElMjAwJTNCJTBBJTdEJTdE”][vc_column width=”1/4″ css=”.vc_custom_1589462584325{padding-top: 0px !important;}”]

what our

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][vc_column width=”3/4″ css=”.vc_custom_1589462588000{padding-top: 0px !important;}”]

With a remarkable track record and an unwavering commitment to excellence, ASNU has established itself as a trusted partner in the automotive industry.
